### SapServer – dev bypass (no JWT required)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5200

### Ping: pool status (admin role auto-granted by DevAuthHandler)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rfc/status

###

### RFC_READ_TABLE – read first 10 rows of T000 (SAP clients table)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rfc/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "functionName": "ZRFC_READ_TABLES",
  "importParameters": {
    "DELIMITER": "|",
    "ROWCOUNT": "10",
    "NO_DATA": " "
  },
  "inputTables": {
    "QUERY_TABLES": [
      { "TABNAME": "T000" }
    ]
  },
  "inputTablesItems": {
      "query_FIELDS": [
        { "TABNAME": "T000", "FIELDNAME": "MANDT" },
        { "TABNAME": "T000", "FIELDNAME": "MTEXT" },
        { "TABNAME": "T000", "FIELDNAME": "ORT01" }
      ]
  },
  "exportParameters": [],
  "outputTables": {
    "data_display":   ["WA"]
  }
}

###

### RFC_READ_TABLE – read USR01 (current user profile), no field filter
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rfc/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "functionName": "RFC_READ_TABLE",
  "importParameters": {
    "QUERY_TABLE": "USR01",
    "DELIMITER": "|",
    "NO_RECS": "5"
  },
  "inputTables": {},
  "exportParameters": [],
  "outputTables": {
    "DATA":   ["WA"],
    "FIELDS": ["FIELDNAME", "OFFSET", "LENGTH", "TYPE"]
  }
}
